         Hey guys, i don't like doing math stuff but it would be nice if someone could show our DPS in the 30 slot scenario, considering, maybe 8 necros, i dont think any 60 guild have 8 level 60 necros but lets consider it cause they will recruit necros after DoT stacking change.</P><P>EDIT: Im not sure if i am correct BUT considering Funeral Pyre, Pyro, Splurt and 20 DPS from pet we get 95.1 DPS x 8 necros = 760.8 DPS. Sounds pretty decent to me. Lets take some DPS out for the time taken to recast the dots and stuff, lets say 700 DPS for 8 Necros. Not the best but very considerable.</P><P>EDIT2: If we use Ebolt + Funeral + Theft of vitae we will have 86.7 DPS + 20 from pet, that makes 106.7 DPS per necro x 8 = 853.6. Round it down to 800.</P><P>Well looking from a guy who doesn't know shit about high end game it sounds pretty good and will raise our value for the high end guilds a lot. What you guys think?</P><P>Onail Aeroc<BR>52 Heretic<BR>Aei'Desis for life<BR>Xegony</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Onail on 08/21/2002  08:02:59</P><P>Edited by - Onail on 08/21/2002  08:03:58</P><P>Edited by - Onail on 08/21/2002  08:11:10<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
