         General warning still about this being on Test.  Things on Test can change without a notice at all.</P><P>As far as slots on a PC go, remember that each additional slot most likely contributes to lag amongst other things.  Briljin and I talked about this for a little while and he came up with an idea (no idea how practical) of scaling slots based on lvl of the NPC.  You would have lvl 65ish NPCs with a heck of a lot of slots and sub 50 NPCs with maybe only 20.</P><P>"Time is meaningless to one who lives forever."<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
